{{Infobox ethnic group 
|group=Hongkongers in the Netherlands<BR/>''Overzeese Hongkongers in Nederland'' 
|population=9,757 (Hong Kong-born)<br />8,440 (Netherlands-born with at least one parent) 
|popplace=[[Amsterdam]], [[Rotterdam]] |languages= [[Dutch language|Dutch]], [[Cantonese language|Cantonese]], [[English language|English]] and [[Hakka language|Hakka]]
|religions = [[Christianity]], [[Buddhism]], [[Confucianism]], [[Taoism]], [[Folk religion]]s |related-c=[[Hongkongers in the United Kingdom]], [[Chinese people in the Netherlands]]
